driver.get("https://google.com");

// open another page
driver.get("https://facebook.com");

// go back
driver.navigate().back();

// go forward
driver.navigate().forward();

// refresh (extra)
driver.navigate().refresh();

Explanation
back() → previous page
forward() → next page
refresh() → reload page

👉 Works same like browser buttons ⬅️➡️
